quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,99,"Kathalika naqussu AAalayka minanba-i ma qad sabaqa waqad ataynakamin ladunna thikra"
  20,100,"Man aAArada AAanhu fa-innahu yahmiluyawma alqiyamati wizra"
  20,101,"Khalideena feehi wasaa lahumyawma alqiyamati himla"
  20,102,"Yawma yunfakhu fee assooriwanahshuru almujrimeena yawma-ithin zurqa"
  20,103,"Yatakhafatoona baynahum in labithtumilla AAashra"
  20,104,"Nahnu aAAlamu bima yaqooloonaith yaqoolu amthaluhum tareeqatan in labithtum illayawma"
  20,105,"Wayas-aloonaka AAani aljibali faqulyansifuha rabbee nasfa"
  20,106,"Fayatharuha qaAAan safsafa"
  20,107,"La tara feeha AAiwajanwala amta"
  20,108,"Yawma-ithin yattabiAAoona addaAAiyala AAiwaja lahu wakhashaAAati al-aswatu lirrahmanifala tasmaAAu illa hamsa"
  20,109,"Yawma-ithin la tanfaAAu ashshafaAAatuilla man athina lahu arrahmanuwaradiya lahu qawla"
  20,110,"YaAAlamu ma bayna aydeehim wamakhalfahum wala yuheetoona bihi AAilma"
  20,111,"WaAAanati alwujoohu lilhayyialqayyoomi waqad khaba man hamala thulma"
  20,112,"Waman yaAAmal mina assalihatiwahuwa mu/minun fala yakhafu thulmanwala hadma"
  20,113,"Wakathalika anzalnahu qur-ananAAarabiyyan wasarrafna feehi mina alwaAAeedilaAAallahum yattaqoona aw yuhdithu lahum thikra"
